    <item>
      <title>加沙停火谈判继续进行，布林肯将访问以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/blinken-set-to-visit-israel-as-gaza-cease-fire-talks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将于本周末访问以色列，结束新一轮关于停止以色列与哈马斯战争的谈判，与此同时，双方官员继续努力阻止伊朗威胁发动袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/blinken-set-to-visit-israel-as-gaza-cease-fire-talks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:20:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰内斯堡自 2016 年以来第十次选举新市长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/johannesburg-elects-new-mayor-for-10th-time-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非最大的政党非洲人国民大会重新夺回约翰内斯堡市长一职，这是该职位自 2016 年以来第十次易主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/johannesburg-elects-new-mayor-for-10th-time-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰继续向库尔斯克地区推进：陆军首席瑟斯基</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/ukraine-continues-advance-into-kursk-region-army-chief-syrskyi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰陆军参谋长奥列克桑德尔·瑟斯基周五在总统电报中发布的视频中向总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基表示，乌克兰军队继续在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区作战，并在一些地区推进了多达 3 公里（1.9 英里）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/ukraine-continues-advance-into-kursk-region-army-chief-syrskyi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:14:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党诉讼针对拜登的 2021 年投票权令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/biden-s-2021-voting-access-order-targeted-by-republican-lawsuits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人瞄准了一项已持续三年的选民登记倡议，旨在将拜登政府拖入法庭斗争，并在美国人投票前几个月对 11 月的选举产生怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/biden-s-2021-voting-access-order-targeted-by-republican-lawsuits</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:54:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友关注其向俄罗斯推进的动向，以寻找最终结局的线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/ukraine-s-allies-watch-its-push-into-russia-for-clues-to-endgame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基辅的盟友大多对乌克兰进攻俄罗斯领土持保留意见，因为对于乌克兰此次试图重绘克里姆林宫两年半战争地图的行动的最终目标尚不确定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/ukraine-s-allies-watch-its-push-into-russia-for-clues-to-endgame</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:14:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大考虑实施点名羞辱政策以遏制虐待外国工人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/trudeau-mulls-name-and-shame-policy-to-curb-foreign-worker-abuse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府正在考虑进行改革，以打击虐待临时外国工人的行为——公开点名违反加拿大劳动法规的企业经理或业主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/trudeau-mulls-name-and-shame-policy-to-curb-foreign-worker-abuse</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 15:53:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪与孟加拉国尤努斯通话，强调少数民族安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/modi-speaks-to-bangladesh-s-yunus-raises-minorities-safety</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪周五与孟加拉国临时政府首脑通了电话。在经历了数周的暴力和纵火事件后，这个陷入困境的南亚国家正在恢复正常。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/modi-speaks-to-bangladesh-s-yunus-raises-minorities-safety</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:46:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多哈回合“建设性”谈判后加沙停火谈判将继续进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/gaza-truce-talks-to-continue-after-constructive-round-egypt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际调解员将在卡塔尔进行为期两天的会谈后恢复以色列与哈马斯之间停火协议的谈判，他们称此次会谈是“严肃且富有建设性的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-16/gaza-truce-talks-to-continue-after-constructive-round-egypt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:25:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
